(838, 193, 'page_who_exapand_component_0_page_who_expand_comp_body', 'Habitat for Humanity of Monroe County is committed to being an equal opportunity employer. Our organization’s policy is to offer equal opportunity to all qualified employees and applicants for employment without regard to race, color, religion, national origin, sex, age, veteran status, disability or other category protected by law. This policy is applicable to recruitment, hiring, rates of pay, job assignments, promotion, training, discipline and all other terms and conditions of employment.\r\n\r\nListed below are our current open positions. To volunteer with us, please visit our volunteer page.'),
