(2806, 263, 'volunteer_sseven_green_block_text', 'To learn more about crew leading or to get involved sign up online or email <a href="mailto:warner@monroecountyhabitat.org">warner@monroecountyhabitat.org</a> to be added to our crew leader email list.\r\n\r\nLearn more now by reviewing our <a href="#">Construction Manual</a>.\r\n'),
