(5118, 333, 'apply_sthree_expands_0_apply_sthree_exapnds_body', 'The Bloomington High School North (BHSN) chapter of Habitat for Humanity was founded in 1998 by students Josh Girvin and Joe Aamidor. It received official independent campus chapter status in 2000 and works in partnership with our affiliate.\r\n\r\nOne of the strongest chapters in the nation, they have co-sponsored a house every year since 2000. In 2017–2018 their 75 members raised nearly $40,000.'),
