(11098, 38, 'waystogive_expands_0_waystogive_expands_body', 'Gifts of Land\r\n\r\nAs the need for affordable housing continues to grow, securing land for homes for the families on our waiting list becomes more challenging. If you are aware of a parcel of land in the county that may be available, we’d like to talk to you.\r\n\r\nWhen we’re able, we purchase land at fair appraisal value. You can help create affordable housing in our community by contacting us if you know of available property or are interested in donating or selling property.\r\n\r\nEmail <a href="mailto:habitat@monroecountyhabitat.org">habitat@monroecountyhabitat.org</a> or call 812-331-4069 for more information.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nHabitat Wish-List on Amazon\r\n\r\nView <a href="https://amzn.com/w/2WTOTV080ZG1F">Habitat’s wish-list</a> of supplies and equipment to facilitate our work to provide decent, affordable housing in our community.\r\n\r\nShopping Programs\r\n\r\nDid you know that simply by buying your groceries you can help our affiliate? By enrolling in our grocery card program you automatically have 3-5% of your grocery spending donated to Habitat for Humanity of Monroe County.\r\n\r\nKroger\r\n– Enroll your Kroger Plus card here\r\n– Use your Kroger Plus Card at the time of purchase to earn rewards\r\n– We receive a reward check every quarter\r\n\r\nAmazon Smile\r\n– Enroll at <a href="https://smile.amazon.com/">smile.amazon.com\r\n</a>– Choose Habitat for Humanity of Monroe County and Amazon will donate 0.5% of the price of your eligible AmazonSmile purchases\r\n\r\nVehicle Donations\r\nDonating a car, truck, boat, RV or other vehicle is quick, easy and may be eligible for tax deduction purposes if you itemize (consult the IRS or tax advisor for details). Cars for Homes (TM) accepts a majority of vehicles with proper title and ownership information, and even makes arrangements to have your vehicle, keys and title picked up for processing.\r\n\r\nProceeds generated by donated vehicle sales are used by us to build homes in partnership with local families.\r\n\r\nFor more information, call 1-877-277-HFHI (4344) toll free or donate online at <a href="http://www.carsforhomes.org">www.carsforhomes.org</a>\r\n\r\nHabitat License Plate\r\n\r\nYou can demonstrate your support for Habitat by ordering a Habitat license plate from the BMV. The plates cost $40, $25 of which goes to our Indiana Habitat for Humanity support organization.\r\n\r\nPlease visit the <a href="http://www.in.gov/bmv/2789.htm">BMV information page</a> for details on ordering your plate.\r\n\r\nFor more information please contact us at <a href="mailto:habitat@monroecountyhabitat.org">habitat@monroecountyhabitat.org</a> or phone at 812-331-4069.'),
