(11182, 38, 'waystogive_expands_4_waystogive_expands_title', 'House Sponsorships'),
(11183, 38, '_waystogive_expands_4_waystogive_expands_title', 'field_5c532ce0e70e1'),
(11184, 38, 'waystogive_expands_4_waystogive_expands_body', 'House sponsors build hope in Monroe County and make an impact for home after home by providing the funding to construct a full  Habitat house. Not only do our partner families benefit from t house sponsorships, but you, your family or your organization will be enriched by the experience.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nSponsorship and partnership are integral to our success and funds provided house sponsors allow us to purchase the “sticks and bricks” to construct homes. Once homeowners begin to pay back their interest-free mortgage, we are able to offer future families an opportunity for home ownership.\r\n\r\nBenefits include::\r\nOpportunity to involve employees in positive, team-building activities\r\nincreased visibility in the community\r\nboost in employee morale\r\n\r\nFaith communities benefit:\r\nopportunity to put faith into action\r\ncreate a deeper fellowship\r\nHouse sponsors have the option to provide volunteers and food as well as the opportunity to spend time with the future homeowner and family.\r\n\r\nHouse Sponsorship Program\r\nThese sponsorship levels relate to the financial commitment made toward the construction of an individual home.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[Table]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nFull House    $70,000+        Sponsor recognition ad\r\n\r\nHalf House    $35,000 – $69,999    Press release announcing build / Joint logo usage\r\nSignage in front of home\r\n\r\nHouse Partner    $17,500 – $34,999    Website recognition\r\nRecognition in Habitat Insider newsletters\r\n\r\nDay Sponsor    $8,750 – $17,499    Name in house dedication program\r\nName in Annual Report\r\n\r\n*Note that benefits are cumulative – in addition to the unique opportunities of each level, the benefits of all previous tiers are included.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nIf you would like to learn more about house sponsorships, please contact 812-331-4069 or email at habitat@monroecountyhabitat.org.'),
