(12014, 434, 'waystogive_expands_1_waystogive_expands_body', 'The <i>More Than Houses Society</i> is critical to our affiliate. The generous pledges from the <i>More Than Houses Society</i> help us cover costs associated with family services, volunteer support, land purchases, infrastructure development, and more. Individual and group members make a long-term commitment to give at least $1,000 per year for five years. Habitat Dream Builders commit to give at least $2,500 per year for five years. In recognition of their loyalty, donors who participate at this giving level are invited to attend appreciation, home tour, and networking events. Join today by donating online or by mail. For questions, please contact us at habitat@monroecountyhabitat.org or 812-331-4069.'),
