(12030, 434, 'waystogive_expands_2_waystogive_expands_body', '$15 per month\r\n\r\nGives a family a strong front door to ensure their safety\r\n\r\n$25 per month\r\n\r\nInsulates a family’s ceiling to keep utility costs affordable\r\n\r\n$35 per month\r\n\r\nTeaches every future homeowner about personal finance, home maintenance, and college readiness\r\n\r\n$55 per month\r\n\r\nSupplies a family with an energy efficient tankless water heater\r\n\r\n$100 per month\r\nBuilds the framework for a roof that brings shelter, warmth, and peace of mind\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nHelp sustain Habitat’s work in Monroe County by becoming a monthly supporter!\r\n\r\nAs a monthly supporter, your donations help uphold and strengthen our ability to serve families in need in Monroe County. Monthly giving is a steady, cost-effective source of income that actually helps reduce administrative costs to the affiliate. This means more of your investment goes directly toward homebuilding and homeowner education, which gives many more deserving families hope for a better future.\r\n\r\nHow it works:\r\n\r\nYou decide how much you would like to give each month. You may stop or alter your payments at any time by calling the office at 812-331-4069 or by emailing <a href="mailto:habitat@monroecountyhabitat.org">habitat@monroecountyhabitat.org</a>\r\n\r\nYou can set up your payment through a credit card or a bank account transfer. Your donation will be charged or transferred around the same time each month. We will send you an annual giving receipt for tax purposes in January each year.'),
